title: 234: 10 Takeaways from Week 11
itunes:title: 234: 10 Takeaways from Week 11
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down their 10 biggest takeaways from this past weekend's action. Is Drew Brees still considered a closer? (10;55). How many more wins does Ben McAdoo need to save his job? (17:50) Is it time to print the Eagles NFC East Champion T-shirts? (27:30) All that and more on this edition of Move the Sticks presented by Ford F-Series.
